{"tid":1466983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈 每個星期六為機場和理飛！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:06.000Z","uid":115194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6721272e121b53ac0a820cd6ffe03fb3a1fc539f","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家依家都擔心緊佔機場仲可唔可行<br />\n所以我正式宣佈 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每星期六為機場和理飛！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日有太多分化黨，不過我相信大家都係有共同目標，就係想<span style=\"color: gold;\">多人到影響到機場運作之餘 又無咁多反對聲音 </span><br />\n<br />\n明白好多人罷唔到工，所以如果每個星期六集會絕對可以好似<span style=\"color: red;\">812咁塞爆機場</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信經過今日後大家可能都對強行阻遊客呢樣嘢反感，所以以人數最勝，係我地最大優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時間亦可以<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">避免旅客濟留係港連續幾日</span></span>，塞左係異地幾日真係好難怪佢地發嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上我地一早大肆宣傳，可以令佢地預早安排下，條氣都順啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每星期一塞</span></span>絕對可以做到好大效果！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">安全，有效果，仲要唔受開學返工限制</span></span>，逼到政府回應為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講句<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 我愛大家 不分化 香港人加油</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地會愈做愈好！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推我上去呀!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"3f6c0be8c1aa2e8eae5eebd36b4ad7fb19a32d33","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:23.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d19469d039867f9e9de68b20ffe2606884f5e872","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"067d810599700cec64c31a3ad1d3f1755f205ed0","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ba103c4b9d3b8f6d1cf032013e872968bb8188d3","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"40551ed00de6cd6a88813013b25577ff3b990abe","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c00382561de6796f4f20e5c8523817c1e69621e0","tid":1466983,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96f51905a2240ddf2cf0357f845f4b181433d39","tid":1466983,"uid":265608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"91520b0f7dbe96eb7ff4693d549a5478f9f503f2","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2b467e104acb3af10f0063c3a2cab10746b165e8","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:48.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"112b785282e8175c80d9c01bffe6f26e2aad7672","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"929aa80d29e145d93bdf742c5b90fb9825d123d0","tid":1466983,"uid":115194,"like":0,"disl